"Category 7: Evaluating test result", "start_offset": "3962", "end_offset": "3982", "annotation_id": "EI_057"}, {"decision": "Droping urine output ", "category": "Category 3: Defining problem", "start_offset": "3984", "end_offset": "4005", "annotation_id": "EI_058"}, {"decision": "Droping urine output responsive to fluid boluses", "category": "Category 5: Drug related", "start_offset": 3984, "end_offset": 4032, "annotation_id": "EI_059"}, {"decision": "fall and head trauma, ? C-spine injury", "category": "Category 3: Defining problem", "start_offset": "4236", "end_offset": "4274", "annotation_id": "EI_060"}, {"decision": "Fall and head trauma and C-spine injury on outside CT and MRI, evaluate fracture.", "category": "Category 3: Defining problem", "start_offset": "4369", "end_offset": "4450", "annotation_id": "EI_061"}, {"decision": "Axial MDCT images were obtained through the cervical spine without intravenous contrast. Additional coronal and sagittal reformations are provided.", "category": "Category 6: Therapeutic procedure related", "start_offset": "4515", "end_offset": "4662", "annotation_id": "EI_062"}, {"decision": "The cervical spine is imaged from C1 through T3. ", "category": "Category 7: Evaluating test result", "start_offset": "4718", "end_offset": "4767", "annotation_id": "EI_063"}, {"decision": "minimally displaced fracture through the spinous process of C4 extending to the posterior arch of C4. ", "category": "Category 3: Defining problem", "start_offset": "4778", "end_offset": "4880", "annotation_id": "EI_064"}, {"decision": "Minimally displaced fractures of the tips of the spinous processes of C5. ", "category": "Category 3: Defining problem", "start_offset": "4880", "end_offset": "4954", "annotation_id": "EI_065"}, {"decision": "Mildly displaced fracture of the spinous process of C7.", "category": "Category 3: Defining problem", "start_offset": "4954", "end_offset": "5009", "annotation_id": "EI_066"}, {"decision": "There is malalignment of the component vertebrae at C4-5, with grade 1 retrolisthesis of C4 on C5 and with marked widening of the intervertebral disc space anteriorly.", "category": "Category 7: Evaluating test result", "start_offset": "5010", "end_offset": "5177", "annotation_id": "EI_067"}, {"decision": "There is additional widening of the intervertebral disc space anteriorly at C6-7.", "category": "Category 7: Evaluating test result", "start_offset": "5178", "end_offset": "5259", "annotation_id": "EI_068"}, {"decision": "There is marked narrowing of the spinal canal at C4-5 due to retrolisthesis of C4 on C5 and angulation of the spine at this level.", "category": "Category 7: Evaluating test result", "start_offset": "5260", "end_offset": "5390", "annotation_id": "EI_069"}, {"decision": "The prevertebral soft tissues are widened diffusely. ", "category": "Category 7: Evaluating test result", "start_offset": "5391", "end_offset": "5444", "annotation_id": "EI_070"}, {"decision": "hematoma", "category": "Category 3: Defining problem", "start_offset": "5629", "end_offset": "5637", "annotation_id": "EI_071"}, {"decision": "In addition, there is a suggestion of hyperdensity within the widened intervertebral disc spaces at C4-5 and C6-7 as well as within the prevertebral soft tissues, possibly representing hematoma.", "category": "Category 7: Evaluating test result", "start_offset": 5444, "end_offset": 5638, "annotation_id": "EI_072"}, {"decision": "nondisplaced fracture", "category": "Category 3: Defining problem", "start_offset": "5860", "end_offset": "5881", "annotation_id": "EI_073"}, {"decision": "There is an additional questionable linear lucency within the anterior inferior aspect of the C2 vertebra on the sagittal views only without clear correlate on the axial views, finding that could represent artifact Vs. a nondisplaced fracture.", "category": "Category 7: Evaluating test result", "start_offset": 5639, "end_offset": 5882, "annotation_id": "EI_074"}, {"decision": "The visualized portions of the lung apices appear unremarkable", "category": "Category 7: Evaluating test result", "start_offset": "5883", "end_offset": "5945", "annotation_id": "EI_075"}, {"decision": "Fractures of the spinous processes at C4, C5, and C7.", "category": "Category 3: Defining problem", "start_offset": "5962", "end_offset": "6015", "annotation_id": "EI_076"}, {"decision": "Cervical spine malalignment of C4-5 and C6-7, with retrolisthesis and intervertebral disc space widening at C4-5 and disc space widening at C6-7, and spinal stenosis. ", "category": "Category 3: Defining problem", "start_offset": "6019", "end_offset": "6186", "annotation_id": "EI_077"}, {"decision": "The findings are highly suggestive of ligamentous injury at these locations. ", "category": "Category 3: Defining problem", "start_offset": "6186", "end_offset": "6263", "annotation_id": "EI_078"}, {"decision": "MRI should be considered for assessment of the spinal cord as well as soft tissues.", "category": "Category 11: Other", "start_offset": "6263", "end_offset": "6346", "annotation_id": "EI_079"}, {"decision": "Marked expansion of the prevertebral soft tissues consistent with hematoma and edema.", "category": "Category 3: Defining problem", "start_offset": "6350", "end_offset": "6435", "annotation_id": "EI_080"}, {"decision": "Questionable artifact Vs. nondisplaced fracture of the anterior inferior corner of C2 vertebra, seen on the sagittal reconstructions only.", "category": "Category 3: Defining problem", "start_offset": "6439", "end_offset": "6577", "annotation_id": "EI_081"}, {"decision": "Results were discussed with the orthopedic resident at the time of interpretation ", "category": "Category 2: Gathering additional information", "start_offset": "6578", "end_offset": "6660", "annotation_id": "EI_082"}, {"decision": "The study and the report were reviewed by the staff radiologist.", "category": "Category 1: Contact related", "start_offset": "6673", "end_offset": "6737", "annotation_id": "EI_083"}, {"dec